==English==

===Etymology===
[[cod]] + [[head]], owing to the [[prevalence]] of [[fishing]] in the area of [[North Shields]] and [[Grimsby]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{cattag|Geordie|pejoratives}} person from [[North Shields]] a town in the northeast of [[England]].
# a person from [[Grimsby]] a [[fishing]] town in the north of [[England]].